---
// HowItWorksPreview — merged HowItWorks + AppPreview
// Design: Dark OLED + Purple, Plus Jakarta Sans, 8px grid
// Pattern: App Store Style — interactive steps control phone screens
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="sl-section" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;">

  <!-- SVG filter: animated water distortion -->
  <svg class="absolute" style="width:0;height:0;" aria-hidden="true">
    <filter id="water-ripple" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%"
            color-interpolation-filters="sRGB">
      <feTurbulence type="turbulence" baseFrequency="0.016 0.046" numOctaves="3" result="noise">
        <animate attributeName="baseFrequency"
          values="0.015 0.044;0.019 0.052;0.015 0.044"
          dur="16s" repeatCount="indefinite"
          calcMode="spline"
          keySplines="0.4 0 0.6 1;0.4 0 0.6 1"/>
      </feTurbulence>
      <feDisplacementMap in="SourceGraphic" in2="noise" scale="14"
        xChannelSelector="R" yChannelSelector="G"/>
    </filter>
  </svg>

  <!-- CSS glow — matches Hero's radial glow -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 right-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"
    style="top:0;height:256px;z-index:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 20%,rgba(145,71,255,0.18) 0%,transparent 70%);"></div>

  <!-- Mirror bars with edge bleed for displacement -->
  <div id="sl-bars-wrap" class="absolute left-0 right-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"
    style="top:-15px;height:271px;z-index:1;overflow:hidden;">
    <!-- SVG filter version — non-iOS -->
    <div id="sl-bars-svg" style="position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;filter:url(#water-ripple);">
      <div class="sl-mirror-bars" style="position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;transform:scaleY(-1);">
        {Array.from({length: 20}).map((_, i) => {
          const pos = i / 19;
          const dist = Math.abs(pos - 0.5) * 2;
          const h = 30 + 70 * Math.pow(dist, 1.3);
          const delay = (i * 0.08).toFixed(2);
          return (
            <div style={`flex:1;height:${h}%;background:linear-gradient(to top,#9147ff,transparent);opacity:0.35;animation:pulseBar 2s ease-in-out ${delay}s infinite alternate;`}></div>
          );
        })}
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Canvas version — iOS Safari only -->
    <canvas id="sl-water-canvas" style="display:none;width:100%;height:271px;"></canvas>
  </div>


  <div class="sl-container" style="position:relative;z-index:3;">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="sl-header">
      <p class="sl-label" id="sl-label">The Loop</p>
      <h2 class="sl-title" id="sl-title">Four steps. Every stream. Forever.</h2>
      <p class="sl-subtitle" id="sl-subtitle">No courses. No fluff. One challenge, one stream, one honest verdict — then repeat.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body: steps + phone -->
    <div class="sl-body">

      <!-- Steps (left on desktop, top on mobile) -->
      <div class="sl-steps">

        <button class="sl-step sl-step--active" data-screen="0">
          <div class="sl-step__num">01</div>
          <div class="sl-step__content">
            <div class="sl-step__header">
              <svg class="sl-step__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="sl-step__title">Get your challenge</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">One mission, picked for your exact level. Not a list of tips — a single thing to focus on this stream.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Personalised to where you actually are</li>
              <li>Based on your weak spots, not generic advice</li>
              <li>Takes 5 seconds to read, one stream to do</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

        <button class="sl-step" data-screen="1">
          <div class="sl-step__num">02</div>
          <div class="sl-step__content">
            <div class="sl-step__header">
              <svg class="sl-step__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="sl-step__title">Stream & upload</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">Go live, do your thing, then screenshot your stats. Drop it in — the AI reads the numbers, you don't type anything.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Twitch, YouTube, Kick, TikTok — any platform</li>
              <li>Just a screenshot — no API, no OAuth</li>
              <li>Done in under 30 seconds</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

        <button class="sl-step" data-screen="2">
          <div class="sl-step__num">03</div>
          <div class="sl-step__content">
            <div class="sl-step__header">
              <svg class="sl-step__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="sl-step__title">See what worked</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">Not "stream more consistently." The AI tells you what broke this stream, what worked, and what your next challenge is.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Specific to your numbers, not generic tips</li>
              <li>What went well, what to fix</li>
              <li>Next challenge unlocks automatically</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

        <button class="sl-step" data-screen="3">
          <div class="sl-step__num">04</div>
          <div class="sl-step__content">
            <div class="sl-step__header">
              <svg class="sl-step__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/>
              </svg>
              <h3 class="sl-step__title">Track your journey</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="sl-step__desc">See where you started, where you are, and what's ahead. Levels, streaks, XP — your whole arc in one place.</p>
            <ul class="sl-step__bullets">
              <li>Levels from "Streaming into the void" to "You made it"</li>
              <li>Weekly streak keeps you consistent</li>
              <li>Watch yourself grow over months</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </button>

      </div>

      <!-- Phone mockup (right on desktop, bottom on mobile) -->
      <div class="sl-phone-wrap">
        <div class="sl-phone-frame">
          <iphone-16-max mode="dark">
            <div id="sl-screens" style="width:100%;height:100%;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#080614;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13px;">

              <!-- ── Screen 0: Home ── -->
              <div class="sl-screen" data-screen="0" style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:#080614;">
                <div style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:36px 14px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;">
                  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;">
                    <div>
                      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">Hey, Marcus 👋</h2>
                      <p style="font-size:11px;color:#64748B;margin:3px 0 0;">Week 4 of your journey</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:50%;background:#7C3AED;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                      <span style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:white;">M</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;">
                    <div style="background:#1C1208;border-radius:12px;padding:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;">
                      <span style="font-size:18px;">🔥</span>
                      <p style="font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;line-height:1;">4</p>
                      <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">WEEK STREAK</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background:#130E28;border-radius:12px;padding:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;">
                      <span style="font-size:18px;">⚡</span>
                      <p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;line-height:1.1;">Lvl 2</p>
                      <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">SOMEONE'S WATCHING</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:12px;padding:10px 12px;">
                    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:5px;">
                      <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">LEVEL PROGRESS</p>
                      <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:#7C3AED;margin:0;">62%</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="height:4px;background:#2A2040;border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;">
                      <div style="width:62%;height:100%;background:#7C3AED;border-radius:2px;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:4px;">
                      <p style="font-size:10px;color:#A78BFA;margin:0;">Someone's watching</p>
                      <p style="font-size:10px;color:#4A4468;margin:0;">Small circle →</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">YOUR CHALLENGE</p>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:12px;padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;">
                    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
                      <span style="background:#7C3AED;color:white;font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;">ACTIVE</span>
                      <span style="font-size:10px;color:#64748B;">STREAM #12</span>
                    </div>
                    <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;line-height:1.35;margin:0;">Go live for 60 minutes without checking your viewer count</p>
                    <p style="font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.4;margin:0;">Anxiety-checking your numbers mid-stream tanks your energy. Your audience can feel it.</p>
                    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
                      <span style="font-size:10px;color:#64748B;">⏱ Ends Sunday</span>
                      <span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#F59E0B;">+150 XP</span>
                    </div>
                    <div style="background:#7C3AED;border-radius:8px;padding:8px;text-align:center;">
                      <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:white;">Mark as Complete</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div style="flex-shrink:0;height:54px;background:#06040F;border-top:1px solid #2A2040;display:flex;align-items:center;">
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#7C3AED" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12L12 3l9 9M5 10v9a1 1 0 001 1h4v-5h4v5h4a1 1 0 001-1v-9"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#7C3AED;font-weight:600;">Home</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Upload</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Analysis</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20v-2a4 4 0 014-4h4a4 4 0 014 4v2"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Progress</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- ── Screen 1: Upload ── -->
              <div class="sl-screen" data-screen="1" style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:none;flex-direction:column;background:#080614;">
                <div style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:36px 14px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
                  <p style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">Upload recap</p>
                  <p style="font-size:11px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">Stream #12 · Just finished</p>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:8px 0 0;">PLATFORM</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;gap:7px;">
                    <span style="background:rgba(124,58,237,0.15);border:1.5px solid #7C3AED;color:#A78BFA;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;">Twitch</span>
                    <span style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;color:#64748B;font-size:11px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;">YouTube</span>
                    <span style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;color:#64748B;font-size:11px;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:8px;">Kick</span>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">ANALYTICS SCREENSHOT</p>
                  <div style="border:1.5px dashed #2A2040;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#100D1C;">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg>
                    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;">Drop your screenshot here</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#4A4A6A;margin:0;">or tap to browse from Photos</p>
                    <p style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;margin:0;">PNG, JPG · Max 10MB</p>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">WHAT TO SCREENSHOT</p>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;">
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Peak viewers, avg viewers, duration</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Follower/subscriber growth</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Chat activity or engagement</p>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;border-radius:10px;padding:11px;text-align:center;">
                    <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#4A4A6A;">Upload a screenshot first</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div style="flex-shrink:0;height:54px;background:#06040F;border-top:1px solid #2A2040;display:flex;align-items:center;">
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12L12 3l9 9M5 10v9a1 1 0 001 1h4v-5h4v5h4a1 1 0 001-1v-9"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Home</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Upload</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Analysis</span></div>
                  <div class="sl-nav-item" style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20v-2a4 4 0 014-4h4a4 4 0 014 4v2"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Progress</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- ── Screen 2: Analysis ── -->
              <div class="sl-screen" data-screen="2" style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:none;flex-direction:column;background:#080614;">
                <div style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:36px 14px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
                  <p style="font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">Stream analysis</p>
                  <p style="font-size:10px;color:#64748B;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.5px;">STREAM #11 · TWITCH · NOV 12</p>
                  <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;">Playing Hollow Knight — First Playthrough</h3>
                  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">8</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">peak viewers</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">3.2</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">avg viewers</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">1h47</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">duration</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">+2</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">followers</p></div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px;">
                    <p style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#22C55E;margin:0 0 4px;">CHALLENGE COMPLETE ✓</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#86EFAC;margin:0;line-height:1.5;">You streamed for 71 minutes without checking. You nailed it.</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#22C55E;margin:4px 0 0;">+150 XP earned</p>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#22C55E;margin:0;">✓ WHAT WENT WELL</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">You held your audience</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Average viewer retention was 40% — solid for your stage.</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">Natural reactions</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Peak moment (8 viewers) came during the boss fight.</p></div>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#F97316;margin:0;">⚠ WHAT TO WORK ON</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">Dead air at the start</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">You lost 2 viewers in the first 8 minutes — talk constantly during loading.</p></div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;border-radius:10px;padding:12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;">
